        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1、创建GitHub仓库"><a href="#1、创建GitHub仓库" class="headerlink" title="1、创建GitHub仓库"></a>1、创建GitHub仓库</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/1.jpg" alt="1"></p><h4 id="配置仓库信息"><a href="#配置仓库信息" class="headerlink" title="配置仓库信息"></a>配置仓库信息</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/2.jpg" alt="2"></p><h4 id="创建成功（仓库界面）"><a href="#创建成功（仓库界面）" class="headerlink" title="创建成功（仓库界面）"></a>创建成功（仓库界面）</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/3.jpg" alt="3"></p><h2 id="2、安装Git"><a href="#2、安装Git" class="headerlink" title="2、安装Git"></a>2、安装Git</h2><h4 id="1、下载Git"><a href="#1、下载Git" class="headerlink" title="1、下载Git"></a>1、下载Git</h4><p>网址：<a href="https://git-scm.com/download/win">https://git-scm.com/download/win</a><br><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/4.jpg" alt="4"></p><h4 id="2、全部默认配置安装"><a href="#2、全部默认配置安装" class="headerlink" title="2、全部默认配置安装"></a>2、全部默认配置安装</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/5.jpg" alt="5"></p><h4 id="3、安装成功"><a href="#3、安装成功" class="headerlink" title="3、安装成功"></a>3、安装成功</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/6.jpg" alt="6"></p><h4 id="4、配置Git"><a href="#4、配置Git" class="headerlink" title="4、配置Git"></a>4、配置Git</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/7.jpg" alt="7"><br>打开C:\Users\NeWer.ssh目录下的id_rsa.pub文件<br><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/8.jpg" alt="8"><br>打开<a href="https://github.com/settings/keys">https://github.com/settings/keys</a><br><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/9.jpg" alt="9"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/10.jpg" alt="10"><br>在Git Bash中检测GitHub公钥设置是否成功，输入 ssh <a href="mailto:&#103;&#105;&#x74;&#x40;&#x67;&#105;&#116;&#x68;&#x75;&#x62;&#x2e;&#x63;&#x6f;&#109;">&#103;&#105;&#x74;&#x40;&#x67;&#105;&#116;&#x68;&#x75;&#x62;&#x2e;&#x63;&#x6f;&#109;</a><br><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/11.jpg" alt="11"><br>创建成功</p><h4 id="5、创建版本库"><a href="#5、创建版本库" class="headerlink" title="5、创建版本库"></a>5、创建版本库</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/13.jpg" alt="13"></p><p>利用Notepad++编写readme.txt文件检验仓库是否可以正常运行<br><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/14.jpg" alt="14"></p><h4 id="bug-1"><a href="#bug-1" class="headerlink" title="bug.1"></a>bug.1</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/Debug.1.jpg" alt="Debug.1"></p><h2 id="3、安装Node-js"><a href="#3、安装Node-js" class="headerlink" title="3、安装Node.js"></a>3、安装Node.js</h2><h4 id="1-1、下载Node-js"><a href="#1-1、下载Node-js" class="headerlink" title="1.1、下载Node.js"></a>1.1、下载Node.js</h4><p>下载地址：<a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/">https://nodejs.org/en/download/</a><br><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/32.jpg" alt="32"></p><h4 id="2-1、安装Node-js"><a href="#2-1、安装Node-js" class="headerlink" title="2.1、安装Node.js"></a>2.1、安装Node.js</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/33.jpg" alt="33"></p><h4 id="2-2、同意协议"><a href="#2-2、同意协议" class="headerlink" title="2.2、同意协议"></a>2.2、同意协议</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/34.jpg" alt="34"></p><h4 id="2-3、选择安装位置"><a href="#2-3、选择安装位置" class="headerlink" title="2.3、选择安装位置"></a>2.3、选择安装位置</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/35.jpg" alt="35"></p><h4 id="2-4、选择安装所需功能"><a href="#2-4、选择安装所需功能" class="headerlink" title="2.4、选择安装所需功能"></a>2.4、选择安装所需功能</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/36.jpg" alt="36"></p><h4 id="2-5、勾选自动安装工具"><a href="#2-5、勾选自动安装工具" class="headerlink" title="2.5、勾选自动安装工具"></a>2.5、勾选自动安装工具</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/37.jpg" alt="37"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/38.jpg" alt="38"></p><h4 id="2-6、完成安装"><a href="#2-6、完成安装" class="headerlink" title="2.6、完成安装"></a>2.6、完成安装</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/39.jpg" alt="39"></p><h4 id="3-1、自动安装所需功能"><a href="#3-1、自动安装所需功能" class="headerlink" title="3.1、自动安装所需功能"></a>3.1、自动安装所需功能</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/40.jpg" alt="40"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/41.jpg" alt="41"></p><h4 id="3-2、安装日志"><a href="#3-2、安装日志" class="headerlink" title="3.2、安装日志"></a>3.2、安装日志</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/42.jpg" alt="42"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/43.jpg" alt="43"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/44.jpg" alt="44"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/45.jpg" alt="45"></p><h4 id="3-3、安装完成"><a href="#3-3、安装完成" class="headerlink" title="3.3、安装完成"></a>3.3、安装完成</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/46.jpg" alt="46"></p><h2 id="4、搭建个人博客"><a href="#4、搭建个人博客" class="headerlink" title="4、搭建个人博客"></a>4、搭建个人博客</h2><h3 id="1、安装Hexo"><a href="#1、安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="1、安装Hexo"></a>1、安装Hexo</h3><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/62.jpg" alt="62"></p><h4 id="1、BUG"><a href="#1、BUG" class="headerlink" title="1、BUG"></a>1、BUG</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/Debug.4.jpg" alt="Debug.4"></p><p>解决方法：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_40954793/article/details/85606605">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_40954793/article/details/85606605</a><br>原因： fsevent是mac osx系统的，在win或者Linux下使用了 所以会有警告，忽略就好了，意思就是你已经安装成功了</p><h4 id="2、BUG"><a href="#2、BUG" class="headerlink" title="2、BUG"></a>2、BUG</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/Debug.5.jpg" alt="Debug.5"></p><p>解决过程：打开VPN（不知道是不是GitHub被墙的缘故），打开网址，找到报错代码<br><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/Debug.5.1.jpg" alt="Debug.5.1"><br><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/Debug.5.2.jpg" alt="Debug.5.2"></p><h4 id="3、安装成功，继续下一步安装"><a href="#3、安装成功，继续下一步安装" class="headerlink" title="3、安装成功，继续下一步安装"></a>3、安装成功，继续下一步安装</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/63.jpg" alt="63"></p><p>顺利安装</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/64.jpg" alt="64"></p><h4 id="4、配置Hexo"><a href="#4、配置Hexo" class="headerlink" title="4、配置Hexo"></a>4、配置Hexo</h4><p>这里仅修改了网站标题</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/65.jpg" alt="65"></p><h3 id="2、Hexo指令"><a href="#2、Hexo指令" class="headerlink" title="2、Hexo指令"></a>2、Hexo指令</h3><h4 id="1、在cmd中输入-hexo-server"><a href="#1、在cmd中输入-hexo-server" class="headerlink" title="1、在cmd中输入 hexo server"></a>1、在cmd中输入 hexo server</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/66.jpg" alt="66"></p><h4 id="2、可在http-localhost-4000（本地）预览网站。"><a href="#2、可在http-localhost-4000（本地）预览网站。" class="headerlink" title="2、可在http://localhost:4000（本地）预览网站。"></a>2、可在<a href="http://localhost:4000（本地）预览网站。">http://localhost:4000（本地）预览网站。</a></h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/67.jpg" alt="67"></p><h4 id="3、生成静态文件"><a href="#3、生成静态文件" class="headerlink" title="3、生成静态文件"></a>3、生成静态文件</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/68.jpg" alt="68"></p><h4 id="4、创建一篇新文章"><a href="#4、创建一篇新文章" class="headerlink" title="4、创建一篇新文章"></a>4、创建一篇新文章</h4><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo <span class="keyword">new</span> page -p miscellaneous/me <span class="string">&quot;About me&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/69.jpg" alt="69"></p><h4 id="BUG"><a href="#BUG" class="headerlink" title="BUG"></a>BUG</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/Debug.6.jpg" alt="Debug.6"></p><p>解决方法：参考<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/u010263423/article/details/106981801">https://blog.csdn.net/u010263423/article/details/106981801</a></p><p>问题分析： Node 版本太高了，我的版本为v14.16.0</p><p>解决方法：换一个低版本Node</p><h4 id="5、部署到GIthub"><a href="#5、部署到GIthub" class="headerlink" title="5、部署到GIthub"></a>5、部署到GIthub</h4><ol><li><h4 id="安装-hexo-deployer-git"><a href="#安装-hexo-deployer-git" class="headerlink" title="安装 hexo-deployer-git."></a>安装 hexo-deployer-git.</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/70.jpg" alt="70"></p></li><li><h4 id="在-config-yml（如果有已存在的请删除）添加如下配置："><a href="#在-config-yml（如果有已存在的请删除）添加如下配置：" class="headerlink" title="在 _config.yml（如果有已存在的请删除）添加如下配置："></a>在 <strong>_config.yml</strong>（如果有已存在的请删除）添加如下配置：</h4></li></ol><p>  <strong>==这里注意repo：后面的地址改为自己的仓库地址==</strong></p><p>  <img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/71.jpg" alt="71"></p><ol start="3"><li><h4 id="运行-hexo-clean-amp-amp-hexo-deploy"><a href="#运行-hexo-clean-amp-amp-hexo-deploy" class="headerlink" title="运行 ==hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo deploy=="></a>运行 ==hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo deploy==</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/72.jpg" alt="72"></p></li><li><h4 id="BUG-1"><a href="#BUG-1" class="headerlink" title="BUG"></a>BUG</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/Debug.7.jpg" alt="Debug.7"></p><p>参考方法：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/liuyongshun2/article/details/54629087">https://blog.csdn.net/liuyongshun2/article/details/54629087</a></p><p>解决方法：可能是==<strong>缩进</strong>==</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/Debug.7.1.jpg" alt="Debug.7.1"></p></li><li><h4 id="问题解决"><a href="#问题解决" class="headerlink" title="问题解决"></a>问题解决</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/Debug.7.2.jpg" alt="Debug.7.2"></p></li><li><h4 id="选择-Sign-in-with-your-browser"><a href="#选择-Sign-in-with-your-browser" class="headerlink" title="选择==Sign in with your browser=="></a>选择==Sign in with your browser==</h4></li><li><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/73.jpg" alt="73"></p></li><li><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/74.jpg" alt="74"></p></li><li><h4 id="https-eatingcrime-github-io-仍然无法进入"><a href="#https-eatingcrime-github-io-仍然无法进入" class="headerlink" title="https://eatingcrime.github.io/仍然无法进入"></a><a href="https://eatingcrime.github.io/%E4%BB%8D%E7%84%B6%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5">https://eatingcrime.github.io/仍然无法进入</a></h4></li></ol><p>   发现问题</p><p>   <img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/75.jpg" alt="75"><br>   <strong>解决方法：</strong>参考<a href="https://1187100546.github.io/2019/11/24/spawn-failed/">https://1187100546.github.io/2019/11/24/spawn-failed/</a></p><p>   与<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/gbz3300255/article/details/97103621">https://blog.csdn.net/gbz3300255/article/details/97103621</a></p><p>   其中的<strong>repo</strong>修改为==git@github.com:yourname/yourname.github.io.git==</p><ol start="10"><li><h4 id="问题解决，上传成功"><a href="#问题解决，上传成功" class="headerlink" title="问题解决，上传成功"></a>问题解决，上传成功</h4></li></ol><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/76.jpg" alt="76"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/77.jpg" alt="77"></p><p>​      再次访问<a href="https://eatingcrime.github.io仍无法进入/">https://eatingcrime.github.io仍无法进入</a></p><p>尝试在终端再次输入==hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo deploy==文章成功访问</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/78.jpg" alt="78"></p><p>这里我个人设置了主题以及一些个性化的配置，效果如下图</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/20210329153651.jpg" alt="100"></p><p>博客网址：<a href="https://eatingcrime.github.io/">https://eatingcrime.github.io/</a></p><h2 id="5、搭建虚拟机"><a href="#5、搭建虚拟机" class="headerlink" title="5、搭建虚拟机"></a>5、搭建虚拟机</h2><h3 id="1、安装VMware"><a href="#1、安装VMware" class="headerlink" title="1、安装VMware"></a>1、安装VMware</h3><h4 id="1-1、下载最新版VMware-Workstation-16-Pro"><a href="#1-1、下载最新版VMware-Workstation-16-Pro" class="headerlink" title="1.1、下载最新版VMware Workstation 16 Pro"></a>1.1、下载最新版VMware Workstation 16 Pro</h4><p>下载地址<a href="https://www.vmware.com/">https://www.vmware.com/</a></p><h4 id="1-2、默认设置安装"><a href="#1-2、默认设置安装" class="headerlink" title="1.2、默认设置安装"></a>1.2、默认设置安装</h4><h3 id="2、使用VMware安装Ubuntu16-04"><a href="#2、使用VMware安装Ubuntu16-04" class="headerlink" title="2、使用VMware安装Ubuntu16.04"></a>2、使用VMware安装Ubuntu16.04</h3><p>参考教程：<a href="http://www.corina.cc/article/51/">http://www.corina.cc/article/51/</a></p><h4 id="2-1-1、下载Ubuntu16-04"><a href="#2-1-1、下载Ubuntu16-04" class="headerlink" title="2.1.1、下载Ubuntu16.04"></a>2.1.1、下载Ubuntu16.04</h4><p>下载地址<a href="http://releases.ubuntu.com/16.04/">http://releases.ubuntu.com/16.04/</a><br><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/12.jpg" alt="12"></p><h4 id="2-2-1、创建虚拟机"><a href="#2-2-1、创建虚拟机" class="headerlink" title="2.2.1、创建虚拟机"></a>2.2.1、创建虚拟机</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/15.jpg" alt="15"></p><h4 id="2-2-2、新建虚拟机向导"><a href="#2-2-2、新建虚拟机向导" class="headerlink" title="2.2.2、新建虚拟机向导"></a>2.2.2、新建虚拟机向导</h4><p><img src="https://gitee.com/eatingcrime/origin-picture/raw/master/img/16.jpg" alt="16"></p><h4 id="2-2-3、硬件兼容性"><a href="#2-2-3、硬件兼容性" class="headerlink" title="2.2.3、硬件兼容性"></a>2.2.3、硬件兼容性</h4><p><img src="https: